ZH: 天主教是世界上最大的基督教宗教之一。
EN: Catholicism is one of the largest branches of Christianity in the world.

ZH: 天主教的信徒相信上帝是三位一体。
EN: Catholics believe in the Holy Trinity - the Father, Son, and Holy Spirit.

ZH: 我们家族传统上都是天主教徒。
EN: Our family has a tradition of being Catholic.

ZH: 天主教总部设在梵蒂冈。
EN: The headquarters of the Catholic Church is located in Vatican City.

ZH: 他们在周日早晨去教堂参加天主教弥撒。
EN: They attend Catholic Mass at church on Sunday mornings.

ZH: 天主教教育注重培养学生的道德价值观。
EN: Catholic education emphasizes the cultivation of students' moral values.

ZH: 我决定信奉天主教并接受洗礼。
EN: I have decided to convert to Catholicism and receive baptism.

ZH: 天主教经文包括《圣经》和教宗的讲话。
EN: Catholic scriptures include the Bible and the speeches of the Pope.

ZH: 天主教的神父通常穿着黑色长袍和领带。
EN: Catholic priests typically wear black robes and collars.

ZH: 他们每年庆祝复活节来纪念耶稣基督的复活。
EN: They celebrate Easter every year to commemorate the resurrection of Jesus Christ.

ZH: 天主教的祈祷在日常生活中扮演着重要角色。
EN: Catholic prayers play an important role in daily life.

ZH: 在天主教仪式中，教堂常常使用圣水和圣油。
EN: Holy water and holy oil are commonly used in Catholic rituals.

ZH: 天主教会鼓励信徒进行慈善捐助和服务他人。
EN: The Catholic Church encourages believers to engage in charitable donations and serving others.

